channel.title: Congratulations to our newest moderator: Si Force
channel.description:
Please welcome our newest member of staff, [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?action=profile;u=117587]Si Force[/url]. He's been very helpful over the last few years. He should have been made a moderator a long time ago. The team will certainly benefit from his presence.
Congratulations Si Force!
